data.description: Exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom corner lot home boasting 1794 square feet of living space. Built in 2015, this meticulously maintained property features and open concept, modern updated kitchen, spacious bedrooms, and an inviting living space. The fireplace provides warmth and coziness during a cold winter day. The primary suite offers a relaxing, private retreat. Backyard oasis perfect for entertaining. Explore comfort and style in this well-crafted home. Solar panels are paid off and the electric bills range from $8.50-$50 or so in the summer months. New refrigerator that will convey to buyer. New master bath shower all glass frameless door, new bathroom fixtures and mirror. Walking distance to the popular 1604 Cantina Food Truck Park. Easy access to Lackland AFB and Alamo Ranch.
